    "body": "Okay on initial investigation i was able to reproduce this issue and  break the UI when I introduce a code block using backticks `` mixed with normal text\r\n\r\nso for example something like this is fine\r\n\r\n`       \r\n SplashScreen splashScreen = SplashScreen.installSplashScreen(this);\r\nsetTheme(R.style.DarkTheme);\r\n// Make sure we get an Alert for every uncaught exceptions\r\nregisterUncaughtExceptionHandler(MainActivity.this);\r\n`\r\n\r\nBut something like this will break \r\n\r\nHere is my splash screen code `       \r\n SplashScreen splashScreen = SplashScreen.installSplashScreen(this);\r\nsetTheme(R.style.DarkTheme);\r\n// Make sure we get an Alert for every uncaught exceptions\r\nregisterUncaughtExceptionHandler(MainActivity.this);\r\n`\r\n\r\n\r\n![Simulator Screen Shot - iPhone 14 Pro - 2023-04-05 at 17 53 15](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/64726664/230079291-cc279699-f93f-47eb-80a8-8ac7ad19a207.png)\r\n",
